over.

30:21.027 --> 30:22.277
[static crackles]

30:25.031 --> 30:26.281
- Any word?

30:26.282 --> 30:28.534
- Nothing so far.

30:34.541 --> 30:36.166
- Lieutenant, come in.

30:36.167 --> 30:37.292
- Yeah. Price here.

30:38.378 --> 30:39.670
- Lieutenant,
we just found his car

30:39.671 --> 30:41.296
about 1/4 mile south of you.

30:42.966 --> 30:44.299
- Any sign of him?

30:46.761 --> 30:48.095
- No.

30:48.096 --> 30:51.098
- Well, fan out and see
if you can flush his ass.

30:53.309 --> 30:54.560
- [sighs]

30:54.561 --> 30:57.563
