Kevin?

32:13.473 --> 32:15.390
He's in the fucking house!

32:15.391 --> 32:16.767
- What the hell?

32:16.768 --> 32:18.226
- He's in the goddamn house!

32:18.227 --> 32:19.895
[pounds]
- Jordan!

32:19.896 --> 32:21.396
- Move! Go! Go!

32:21.397 --> 32:22.606
Haul your ass!

32:22.607 --> 32:23.815
- Price!

32:23.816 --> 32:25.692
- Jordan?

32:27.403 --> 32:28.445
Get the door.

32:28.446 --> 32:30.030
